Not much is known about the agent code-named Arcibi, aside from his involvement in the SCP projects and the fact that he led a garage band in his high-school years known as "Captain Cactus and the Water Preservation Squad".

Arcibi is credited with discovering the following SCP items:

[[[ SCP-127]]] - The Living Gun
[[[SCP-294]]] - The Coffee Machine
--SCP-627-J-- - The Companion Cube
